ActQalipu Mi'kmaq First Nation Act
SubjectOrder Amending the Qalipu Mi’kmaq First Nation Band Order
PrecisOrder Amending the QALIPU MI'KMAQ FIRST NATION BAND ORDER in order to specify that the members of the Qalipu Mi'kmaq First Nation are the individuals identified on the list of founding members provided by the Enrolment Committee to the Federation of Newfoundland Indians and to the Government of Canada on November 7, 2022.
